Ing '''Danyang''' ([[Simplified Chinese]]: 丹阳市; [[Traditional Chinese]]: 丹陽市; [[pinyin]]: Dānyáng Shì) metung yang [[lakanbalen a kadaneng kondadu]] (''county-level city'') a sakup ning [[Zhenjiang]] king lalawigan ning [[Jiangsu Province]] king [[Maldang Republika ning Tsina]]. Nanupata, atyu king pilatan ning Zhenjiang ampong [[Changzhou]], at pareu ya daya kareng adwang deti, at mas malagwa yang dasan manibat king Changzhou kesa king Zhenjiang.  

Anyang [[Southern and Northern Dynasties#The Southern Dynasties|Southern Dynasties]], tubu reng balen ding dakal a pamilyang ari ning  [[Southern Qi]] ampong [[Liang Dynasty|Liang]] Dynasties.  Uli na niti, milibing la keti deng emperador ampong prinsipi da reng pamilyang aring deti kareng mapanagaulang misnang penagaulang libingan. Ngeni, mas pikabaluan ya king pamangawang lenting para salamin ampong sunglass.  

Anyang 2012, mika bayu yang rutang tren ing Danyang, ing North Station (Bei Zhan), king [[Beijing–Shanghai High-Speed Railway|Shanghai to Beijing high-speed railway line]], anya malyari nang maglakbe manibat king Danyang angga king Istasyung Hongqiao ning Shanghai kilub na mu ning metung a oras ampong apulung minutu. Atin muring bayung istasyung tren para king byahi papunta king sentru ning lakanbalen.  

Maki pangkabilugan yang lapad a 1,059&nbsp;km<sup>2</sup> ing Danyang. Magsalita lang dayalektu ning [[Wu]] deng memalen ning Danyang, at atyu ing lakanbalen king angganan ning Wu ampo ning Jianghuai [[Mandarin Chinese|Mandarin]].

